96S2yKxQEoaMBOAbg">Quá Quách đại công cố trạch - 過郭代公故宅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-U5c-0DQVYYShqCiOxuDe9w">Thất tịch - 七夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%C3%A1c/author-e0otN6vCPPdd_j1RD4YdLg">Dương Phác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/T%C3%ADch-hoa/poem-OyPgnjg3EcvtCt6tBgYaXw">Tích hoa - 惜花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/Trung-thu-ngo%E1%BA%A1n-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-ofQBfBk75T4Bwjt8ACW4kg">Trung thu ngoạn nguyệt - 中秋翫月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/author-RGxtMe1sV6AuAbjteu9Sdg">Jingak Hyesim</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Li%C3%AAm/Vi%E1%BB%87t-ca/poem-WEJuJvnN-wODOEYeXse6lg">Việt ca - 越歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Li%C3%AAm/author-cJEa_nnPF2Dm3ze1rqMDcA">Tống Liêm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
